Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 5.0°C) and outside temperature (up 3.9°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 9%) and rainfall (up 0.3 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 603 m) and light levels (up 2851 lux).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 1007 m) and light levels (up 6599 lux) when compared to today.
